+- `[VERIFIED]` The exact Fourier/Leray law every candidate is tracking is
+
+  ```text
+  ∂t û(k) + |k|^2 û(k)
+    = -i ∑_{p+q=k} (q · û(p)) P_k û(q),
+  P_k = I - (k ⊗ k)/|k|^2,
+  û(-k) = overline{û(k)}.
+  ```
+
+- `[INFERRED]` On a canonical helical sheet
